window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Wedding plans, eldritch conspiracies, and renovation projects–life is never easy.</b></p> <p>When I bound myself to a rundown magical manor, I never expected I’d become a mighty hearthomancer, warden of an imprisoned demon and protector of Earth. Still, it worked out pretty well. I’ve got a few side hustles opening up, rent income is steady, and wedding bells are in the air.</p> <p>But now, some jerk who calls him Damnation’s Architect is trying to ruin everything. He’s been conspiring for centuries to destroy my home and bring about the apocalypse. It’s up to me and my brides-to-be to save the day.</p> <p><b>Everything is going to be—WAIT, MY MOM HEARD ABOUT MY ENGAGEMENT?!? I’M SCREWED</b></p>"; 
